                                                         text-align:left">
                                                            Enter ideal body size high measurement  Or  Ideal body size low measurement greater than 0
                                                         </div>
                                       
                                                <div id="error_valid_ideal_body_size_high" style="display:none;color: #DD1144;font-size: 0.8em;
